Package: mlpdataintro
Type: Package
Title: MLP Data Introduction: Tracking Civic Space in Developing Countries
Version: 1.0.0
Description: This package provides data and analysis tools for tracking civic space 
    in developing countries using a high-quality corpus of domestic media and 
    transformer models. The dataset covers 65 developing countries across regions: 
    Eastern Europe/Central Asia, MENA, Latin America & Caribbean, East Asia, and 
    Sub-Saharan Africa. It includes both civic events (20 categories) and regional 
    and international (RAI) influence events (22 categories) extracted from 
    international, regional, and local news sources.
